The paper deals with image synthesis using Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs), which is a popular topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also proposes a new technique for addressing the instability during training, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of multiple scales in image synthesis is also related to computer graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
